Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Assigned' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to transition from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes to move from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Closed' for cases involving 'PROD582'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases with 'Medium' impact compared to 'High' impact cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'Medium' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - User' in cases with 'Low' impact
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'High' impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that do not follow the most common process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases initiated by 'V30' org:group
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' for cases involving 'PROD321'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that transition directly to 'Completed + Closed' without 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases with 'Medium' product impact compared to those with 'High' product impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'Medium' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Assigned' and the next activity for cases exceeding the average duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in the top 10 longest cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average time to complete 'Accepted + Assigned' for products with more than 10 occurrences in the log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to complete 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that required reassignment to a different 'org:resource'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case
